{"tid":759276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞馬遜和軟銀想推動日本無現金化","createTime":"2018-07-28T12:42:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T19:07:30.000Z","uid":141151,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a8a500f452584e0f5ab2d3da9718c8a10703b497","tid":759276,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:42:33.000Z","msg":"亞馬遜和軟銀想推動日本無現金化<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3277774\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F3277774&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0belKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=c72ac776\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3277774</a><br />\n<br />\n電商巨擘亞馬遜和軟體銀行將於接下來幾個月，雙雙在日本推出智慧手機支付服務，力圖爭取小型企業的青睞。日本仍極度仰賴現金交易，小型企業在推廣行動支付方面因此處於關鍵地位。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜和軟銀提供的行動支付平台僅須商家進行極小額的投資，這種方式對小型企業來說較友善，小型企業估計占日本商店約90%，而對他們來說，取得特定的設備是項沉重的負擔。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜將透過在日本的分支「亞馬遜日本」（Amazon Japan）推廣Amazon Pay支付服務，讓前往實體零售商店消費的日本消費者能將信用卡與他們在亞馬遜網站的帳戶相連。負責結帳的店員將用平板電腦直接掃描消費者智慧手機的QR碼，省去處理信用卡或請消費者簽名的麻煩。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜計劃與無現金支付服務商Nippon Pay合作，下個月在福岡市試行Amazon Pay。<br />\n<br />\n軟銀則在27日表示，將和印度的支付服務商Paytm與雅虎日本合作，最快會在今年秋天推出行動支付服務。軟銀推出的行動支付服務讓消費者和商家都能掃描另一方的QR碼。<br />\n<br />\n在日本，即便包含信用卡交易，無現金支付仍僅占該國交易約20%。相較之下，此比率在南韓約達90%，在中國則約為60%。日本政府計劃在2027年前，將全國的無現金支付占比提高至40%"},{"pid":"7949084b24f58a0e547b1b21100ef5093000f617","tid":759276,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T12:54:20.000Z","msg":"日本鬼子好落後"},{"pid":"afdb2dc0312b2b4a5202b2186631153e943f5620","tid":759276,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T13:07:55.000Z","msg":"等比日本人抵制"},{"pid":"ee1b7902db7c3991db8a0bb0bb02add79a238de0","tid":759276,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T13:59:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d9a6d863f83f3d19ab49db4d885f1347c300b80","tid":759276,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"又話支那好先進得40%？"},{"pid":"209e5371f89b445bd6f2471bc335231339e909d6","tid":759276,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話支那好先進得<span style=\"color: red;\">60</span>%？</blockquote>"},{"pid":"e1afc9c02494a72428e951f3ead84b91e684498a","tid":759276,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"209e5371f89b445bd6f2471bc335231339e909d6","tid":759276,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話支那好先進得<span style=\"color: red;\">60</span>%？</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:09:12.000Z","msg":"金管局：港電子支付成熟 佔私人消費六成　銀行界：信用卡簽帳為主<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170825/s00004/1503597538882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170825%2Fs00004%2F1503597538882&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0belKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=7dbc840e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170825%2Fs00004%2F1503597538882&h=cca42425\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170825/s00004/1503597538882</a><br />\n<br />\n香港都係六成"},{"pid":"211b38a1ee284f5ca30197eb00a13f41cc1134a7","tid":759276,"uid":85116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"無現金化,會唔會對黑錢會有咩影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1d3a8e3384afdc5755e75c79d70e59536a6db3","tid":759276,"uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e1afc9c02494a72428e951f3ead84b91e684498a","tid":759276,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"209e5371f89b445bd6f2471bc335231339e909d6","tid":759276,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:04:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又話支那好先進得<span style=\"color: red;\">60</span>%？</blockquote>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:09:12.000Z","msg":"金管局：港電子支付成熟 佔私人消費六成　銀行界：信用卡簽帳為主<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170825/s00004/1503597538882\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170825%2Fs00004%2F1503597538882&d=dy%2FRrdHMVvVmQJii9%2F0belKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=7dbc840e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170825%2Fs00004%2F1503597538882&h=cca42425\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170825/s00004/1503597538882</a><br />\n<br />\n香港都係六成"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T17:54:14.000Z","msg":"香港人concept：信用卡、八達通、APPLE PAY、PAY WAVE ETC. 都係無現金消費<br />\n<br />\n支那狗concept：只有掃QR code先係無現金消費, 唔掃QR code就係好落後<br />\n<br />\n支那狗真係生番一樣既思維黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38fd2af029c172026ecf2357418645a84e50337","tid":759276,"uid":19211,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T19:07:30.000Z","msg":"係日本用現金方便好多<br />\n唔似香港大紙唔收碎銀唔收呢樣唔講啦，<br />\n銀包的鈔票通常只有10000yen和1000yen<br />\n(5000比較少見，2000稀有過香港10蚊青蟹)<br />\n<br />\n硬幣每一款都係唔同色唔同紋，<br />\n一開銀包就分得到(除左100yen同50yen側面比較難分)<br />\n<br />\n仲有呀，去過日式玩相信都知他們的自動販賣機覆蓋率有幾高，<br />\n佢地認硬幣貨幣出錯率低過香港多多聲，<br />\n去JR買飛你甚至可以成袋銀包的鈹到落去，<br />\n佢多出來的會跌返出黎。<br />\n<br />\n最後，日本都好多店舖有輕觸支付(iD, QUICPay, Edy)<br />\n相比起香港用visa master要等銀行approved，<br />\n佢地係完全唔使等，有suica的地方又可以用suica"}]}